1. login to Salesforce.com and navigate toSetup | Administer | Manage Users | Users.
2. Click on Users button as shown above.
3. Click on New User 
4. When creating a new user in Salesforce it is important to assign Roles, User license and Profile to the new user.
Note :- Username in Salesforce must be in Email address format and unique.
5. Enter First name, last name, Alias, Email address.
6. Now Assign a Role to the user.
7. Now assign user license to the new user.
8. Assign a profile to the user.
9. Now select generate passwords and notify user via email.
10. Click on Save button.
11. A verification email will be sent to the Email.
